<td width="10"><img src="http://www.maximumeq.com/forum/Images/Message.gif" border="0"></td><td width="100%"><font face="Verdana" size="2" color="000000"> <b>Mages, a forgotten class, a dying race</b> <img src="http://www.maximumeq.com/forum/Images/New.gif" border="0"></font></td></tr></table></td></tr><tr bgcolor="EEEEEE">
<td><font face="Verdana" size="1" color="000000">mage balancing</font></td></tr></table></td></tr></table><p><table width="100%" border="0" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0" align="CENTER" bgcolor="000000">
